 > This project is still ongoing, my hope is add data analysis tools and apply them to the stock data.
 > Users will be allowed to purchase, sell, or even trade stocks based on their budget.
+
+## API keys
+
+API keys are stored in the local SQLite database so they are still available after the server restarts.
+
+Create the database tables:
+
+```bash
+python -c "from models import db; db.create_all()"
+```
+
+Save the IEX API key:
+
+```bash
+python manage_api_keys.py set iex YOUR_IEX_API_KEY
+```
+
+List saved API key providers:
+
+```bash
+python manage_api_keys.py list
+```
+
+The app also supports `IEX_API_KEY` as a fallback environment variable if no key has been saved in the database yet.
